Package: textwork
Type: Package
Title: Clean webscrapped text
Version: 0.0.1.0
Author: Eugen Toews
Maintainer: Eugen Toews <eugtoews@gmail.com>
Description: The cleanString function removes special characters and punctuation that are irrelevant to the text analysis.
    Moreover, it repairs uncommon characters from special fonts and includes an empty space after the full stop at the end of a sentence.
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0.9000
